'''謝潑德·史密斯'''（Shepard Smith，{{bd|1964年|1月14日}}）是[[美國|美國]]的一位電視新聞主播。他曾經擔任Fox Report節目的主播。2013年10月開始，他出任Shepard Smith Reporting節目的主持。史密斯出生在密西西比州<ref name="ppl030428">{{cite journal |url=http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20139878,00.html |title=Cable King |journal=People |first=Jason |last=Lynch |volume=59 |issue=16 |date=April 28, 2003 |accessdate=July 22, 2009 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304043803/http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20139878,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ajr1001">{{cite news |url=http://www.ajr.org/Article.asp?id=4841 |title=The Anti-Anchor |work=American Journalism Review |first=Sherry |last=Ricchiardi |date=January 2010 |accessdate=December 8, 2009 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131027112410/http://www.ajr.org/article.asp?id=4841 |archive-date=2013-10-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="destin20090713">{{cite news |url=http://www.thedestinlog.com/articles/news-10033-destin-shephard.html |title=How Destin Hardee's helped launch Shephard Smith to Studio B at Fox News |work=The Destin Log |first=William |last=Hatfield |date=July 13, 2009 |accessdate=December 9, 2009 |archive-date=2012-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120219095723/http://www.thedestinlog.com/articles/news-10033-destin-shephard.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，曾就讀於密西西比大學並主修新聞學。他主持的Fox Report是美國有線電視收視率最高的新聞節目之一。他還客串出演過電影。
